== 傷殘人士設施 ==

該站以行人隧道通往街外，但不設升降機等傷殘人士設施。車站在開放時間會在職員當值。<ref>{{cite web en|work=City Rail|title=Banksia station facilities|url=http://www.cityrail.info/stations/station_details?stationId=73|accessdate=28 June 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101125214324/http://cityrail.info/stations/station_details?stationId=73|archive-date=2010-11-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

